<h2>LessonBuilder: Overview</h2>
<h3>Introduction</h3>
<p>Lesson Builder is a way to structure content. Use cases include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Online courses, which often want to structure material by unit or week. It must be easy to link to quizzes and assignments, and to handle common types of content.</li>
    <li>Online training, which needs to define sequences of material.</li>
    <li>Online certification, which needs to require certain items to be done, and sometimes to limit access until prerequisites are met.</li>
    <li>Import of publisher content or content from other systems that support Common Cartridge (import only at the moment).</li>
</ul>

<p>Use the action buttons at the top of the page to add content.</p>

<h3>How Do I?</h3>

<p> Tools that allow you to add content to a page: </p>

<ul>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddText">Add text or HTML content to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddResources">Add resources (resources shown as web links) to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddMultimedia">Add multimedia (resources shown in a box on the page) to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddAssignments">Add assignments to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddQuizzes">Add quizzes to a page</a></li>
</ul>

<p> The following functions appear in a separate menu "More tools:"</p>

<ul>

<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddTopics">Add forum topics to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddSubpages">Add additional pages (e.g. subpages) to a page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolReorganize">Reorganize content</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolComments">Allow students to add comments</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolStudentContent">Allow students to add their own pages</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolExternal">Add external web service using IMS Basic Learning Tool Interoperability protocol</a></li>
</ul>

<p> Other functions: </p>

<ul>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolSettings">Change page settings</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolRemove">Remove Top-level Page</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolAddTop">Add Top-level Page(s)</a></li>
<li><a href="content.hlp?docId=lessonbuildertoolCCImport">Load file in Common Cartridge Format</a></li>
</ul>


